query: select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, PerC.Phenotype OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and substring(RIGHT('000000' + cast(PerC.Phenotype as varchar(6)),6), 1, 1) = '0' and substring(RIGHT('000000' + cast(PerC.Phenotype as varchar(6)),6), 2, 5) not like '%0%' and substring(RIGHT('000000' + cast(PerC.Phenotype as varchar(6)),6), 1, 2) != '11' and substring(RIGHT('000000' + cast(PerC.Phenotype as varchar(6)),6), 5, 2) != '11'
